Class PersonalityInsights

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.service.WatsonService
      • com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.personality_insights.v2.PersonalityInsights

  • public class PersonalityInsights
extends WatsonService
    The Watson Personality Insights service uses linguistic analytics to extract a spectrum of cognitive and social characteristics from the text data that a person generates through blogs, tweets, forum posts, and more.
    Version:
    v2

    • Method Detail

      • getProfile

        public ServiceCall<Profile> getProfile(String text)
        Accepts text and responds with a Profile with a tree of characteristics that include personality, needs, and values.

        Here is an example of how to get the personality profile given some text: 
             PersonalityInsights service = new PersonalityInsights();
     service.setUsernameAndPassword("username", "password");

     String text = "write the text with at least 100 unique words here..."
     Profile profile = service.getProfile(text).execute();
     System.out.println(profile);
        Parameters:
        text - Text to analyze
        Returns:
        The personality Profile

      • getProfile

        public ServiceCall<Profile> getProfile(ProfileOptions options)
        Returns a Profile with a tree of characteristics that include personality, needs, and values.

        Here is an example of how to get the personality profile given some ProfileOptions: 
             PersonalityInsights service = new PersonalityInsights();
     service.setUsernameAndPassword("username", "password");

     String text = "write the text with at least 100 unique words here..."
     ContentItem cItem = new ContentItem().content(text).created(new Date());
     ProfileOptions options = new ProfileOptions().contentItems(Arrays.asList(cItem));

     Profile profile = service.getProfile(options).execute();

     System.out.println(profile);
        Parameters:
        options - the ProfileOptions
        Returns:
        The personality Profile
